Before using this software in a production healthcare environment:

1. Conduct a thorough security assessment
2. Implement required operational procedures
3. Ensure physical security measures
4. Complete a HIPAA risk assessment
5. Obtain legal review and approval
6. Implement Business Associate Agreements (BAAs)
7. Conduct regular security audits
8. Implement incident response procedures
9. Ensure proper staff training
10. Maintain comprehensive documentation

